Package: nytindia
Title: Prepare and visualize India-tagged data from the NYT Article Search API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sean",
           family = "Angiolillo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sean.angiolillo@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package includes functions to query the 
    Article Search API of The New York Times for articles with 
    an India location keyword. It includes functions to prepare 
    this data to be ready for analysis and visualization. 
    It includes a shiny app to interact with the output datasets. 
